{"tid":1281080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[各位有夢遊中學生唔洗驚]班狗放咁多on9風即係根本拉唔撚到人","createTime":"2019-07-03T07:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T10:27:14.000Z","uid":33775,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9934cafeb86fc277b44480ce9309e1165f4f5c62","tid":1281080,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:37:42.000Z","msg":"知你地好大壓力，我讀中學果陣比老師兇兩兇都已經好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班狗就知道你地呢一種心理，呢2日瘋狂放風話大型搜證<br />\n但冷靜d諗清楚，如果佢地真係可以係立會入面搵撚到你指紋，或者真係cctv拉人<br />\n佢地洗乜係報紙通晒天，一早拉撚左你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你諗下立會同時有幾多個人嘅指紋，佢憑D咩可以拉到你嘅完整指紋<br />\n重有係唔同地區亂鳩咁拉人，琴晚柴灣單野擺明有心搞大佢等你地驚到仆街<br />\n之後每幾個鐘就搵東方星島出一出係邊度邊度拉左人嘅新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得做好應嘅保護，DEL晒唔應該比人見到嘅野，如果真係好驚就去旅行（去台灣日本果D就算即日機票都係幾千蚊內），咁就足夠，千祈唔好比班狗兇到影響正常生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615fe56ef01b0b6e4fc6ce1d00678b1454edb2e1","tid":1281080,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:15:56.000Z","msg":"希望你地睇到"},{"pid":"6fcd2878f106056a331abe23dc21f2321ec2d637","tid":1281080,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:22:12.000Z","msg":"推，拉到一早拉左而吾係出小人手段"},{"pid":"89cbc78c99945e073e88ccd76873f699a66bbcb0","tid":1281080,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:34:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284f7bf5405daca634a047d4f1d09728b346695d","tid":1281080,"uid":80139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:36:42.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n就算真係拉你入狗屋記住「我無野講」"},{"pid":"032b9c342d44ce125f7b9f257c0fefc9dd65dce0","tid":1281080,"uid":33775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:36:57.000Z","msg":"班狗走去拉人放個人資料都唔拉唔到在場義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ad74830f85544948acff1fd70c51aa5fb17f1d","tid":1281080,"uid":158317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:38:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>推 <br />\n而家就係想宣揚白色恐怖<br />\n你覺得警犬班垃圾會做到嘢？<br />\n嚇下你地咋 等你以後唔好出黎<br />\n唔係信ar</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"969d5df994205ff70205106ee3a4890d7479262b","tid":1281080,"uid":259423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:40:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fda7aa20565cace76349608f1040a7d96a794834","tid":1281080,"uid":272964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:40:43.000Z","msg":"堅"},{"pid":"38408bca0d09bc1d34faf3c3eaf92a11d886003b","tid":1281080,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0272501db2073c80493666fc38199eb1d531a6","tid":1281080,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}